    narr:generatedFrom "f1b43fa2ace055d7bf08068ca6e6c791b8625331" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolution of organizations as steerable, generative systems. The conceptual foundation rests on [flocking simulations](narr:Observation_FlockingInsight) and the 2019 thesis that [LLMs are continuation machines](narr:Narrative_LLMsContinuation) rather than thinkers, establishing [narrative as a steering vector](narr:Narrative_SteeringVector). Industrial precedents like [Harmony Labs](narr:Narrative_HarmonyLabs) and [Aspen](narr:Narrative_Aspen) inform the approach to language-as-code. 

Recent development has shifted toward the [Agent Computer Interface](narr:Narrative_AgentComputerInterface), which frames the boundary between human and agent agency as the core design problem. This is supported by an [MCP-agnostic architecture](narr:Position_MCPAgnostic) now validated in production, alongside [Front App](narr:Narrative_FrontHITLSubstrate) for coordination, [Vouch.io](narr:Narrative_VouchIdentityForAgents) for security, and [perspective shares](narr:Narrative_PerspectiveShares_Distribution) for distribution. The [long-tail perspective farming](narr:Narrative_LongTailPerspectiveAutomation) model, which automates advisor interviews, represents a move toward scaling these systems. Emerging threads include a [neurosymbolic marriage](narr:Narrative_NeurosymbolicKGLLM) of knowledge graphs and LLMs, and a [Fireflies-based transcription pipeline](narr:Obs_FirefliesWebhookQuote) for data ingestion.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AgentComputerInterface> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_Aspen> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CrossPlatformValidation> ;
